title: What is Demand Avoidance? A Guide for Teenagers
description:
This mini-course is for teenagers to watch themselves.
It explains why sometimes, everything feels like pressure and the more others try to help you, the harder it is to do anything, even things you’d like to do. It helps teens think about how to build a life which works for them.
It’s suitable for anyone who experiences demand avoidance, whether or not they have a diagnosis.
